@marksandspencer Coffee boy at your service! 
 FREE hot drinks anyone?! I spent the day at M&S London Colney this week in the cafe serving up FREE hot drinks ...  It was exhausting - M&S baristas you are next level! 
 
Did you know that when you sign up for the hot drink’s loyalty stamp in your M&S Sparks account - when you’ve bought your 6th hot drink, the 7th will be FREE! Yes absolutely FREE - and who doesn’t love a freebie! You can scan the QR code on the cafe posters to take you directly to the sign-up or head to marksandspencer.com/coffee-stamps -  ‘cos the best drinks in life are free! #Ad #Thisisnotjust

